###  http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9#ActiveImplant
:ActiveImplant rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                        :Device ;
               :isSubclassifiedUnder :ImplantableDevice .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9#ClassIII
:ClassIII rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                   :RiskClass .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9#ClassIIa
