:ClassIIb rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                   :RiskClass ;
          :isSubclassifiedUnder :ClassIII .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9#ImplantableDevice
:ImplantableDevice rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
